        "description": "<a href='https://www.microsoft.com/legal/terms-of-use'> Azure's terms of use </a> prohibit the use of Azure services in ways that could damage, disable, overburden, or impair any Microsoft server or the network. This recommendation lists exposed ports that need to be closed for your continued security. It also illustrates the potential threat to each port.",
